By leveling up

Level Ability Cost Description
1 Blaze 3 Powers up Fire-type moves when the Pokémon's HP is low.
10 Heatproof 2 The heatproof body of the Pokémon halves the damage from Fire-type moves that hit it.
25 Illuminate 2 Raises the Pokémon's evasiveness.
40 Flame Body 3 Contact with the Pokémon may burn the attacker.
55 Flash Fire 3 Powers up the Pokémon's Fire-type moves if it's hit by one.
70 White Smoke 5 The Pokémon's white smoke prevents other Pokémon from lowering its stats.
85 Solar Power 5 Boosts the Sp. Atk stat in harsh sunlight or solar wind, but HP decreases every turn.
100 Dragon's Maw 3 Powers up Dragon-type moves.
  • Bold indicates a default ability if multiple abilities are disabled
  • Italic indicates hidden ability if multiple abilities are disabled
